---
description: Token optimization
alwaysApply: true
---

- Never scan the full repository unless explicitly requested
- Read only files directly related to the current task
- Avoid opening dependency files unless necessary
- Avoid repeated reads of the same files
- Prefer minimal diffs
- Prefer editing existing code over rewriting files
- Keep answers under 150 words unless asked
- Avoid generating unnecessary explanations
- Ask before making multi-file refactors
- Do not inspect tests unless the task involves tests
- Do not inspect documentation unless requested